<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">群员管理制度，不管是群管理员还是群员都必须严格遵守的制度。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">俗话说的好：“没有规矩，不成方圆”为了营造一个和谐、文明的公共交流平台，请群成员务必遵守如下条例：</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">新、老群友务必查看此群规，我们将严格按照群规执行，如有人因违反以下<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">1</SPAN>—<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">6</SPAN>条群规被踢或被加黑请不要不满。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">1</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、未经允许不得在群内进行商业广告行为<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">;</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">2</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、群内禁止发黄色性的广告；。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">3</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、严禁对女性恶意骚扰<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">;</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">4</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、不能利用本群制作、复制和传播违法内容<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">;</SPAN></SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">5</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、不能宣扬封建迷信、淫秽、色情、赌博、暴力、凶杀、恐怖、教唆犯罪的<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">;</SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 32pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312" XML:LANG="EN-US">6</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt; FonT-FAMiLY: 仿宋_GB2312">、不能侮辱他人或者捏造事实诽谤他人，或者进行其他恶意攻击。</SPAN></P>
